    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Alpha Diversity\"\nauthor:\n  - name: Muluh\nparams: \n  index: default\n---\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n## Group-wise comparisons\n\n-   **Index:** observed\n-   **Group variable:** diet\n-   **Multiple testing correction:** FDR\n-   **Statistical test** Wilcoxon\n\nIn the report, a suffix of 1~ Baseline and 2~ Week 6\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](alpha_observed_files/figure-html/visualize-plot-1.png){fig-align='center' width=480}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n### Table of the top findings\n\n#### Across-group\n\n##### Before treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **FDR**\n-   Statistical test: **Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-844cda400e4ce0bf4040\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-844cda400e4ce0bf4040\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of alpha diversity comparisons at the Baseline<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\"],[\"rice\"],[211.2],[231.6],[0.13],[0.128]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>group1<\\/th>\\n      <th>group2<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.adj<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[2,3,4,5]},{\"name\":\"group1\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"group2\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":4},{\"name\":\"p.adj\",\"targets\":5}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[6,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n##### After treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **FDR**\n-   Statistical test: **Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-2132a4f07df90820af38\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-2132a4f07df90820af38\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of alpha diversity comparisons at Week 6<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\"],[\"rice\"],[207.1],[233.3],[0.17],[0.049]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>group1<\\/th>\\n      <th>group2<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.adj<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[2,3,4,5]},{\"name\":\"group1\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"group2\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":4},{\"name\":\"p.adj\",\"targets\":5}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[6,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](alpha_observed_files/figure-html/viz-div_change-1.png){fig-align='center' width=480}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n#### Within-group\n\n##### Paired treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **FDR**\n-   Statistical test:  **paired Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-b46c00eb4e2f92cac3d9\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-b46c00eb4e2f92cac3d9\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of alpha diversity paired between the Baseline and Week 6<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\",\"rice\"],[211.2,231.6],[207.1,233.3],[0.04,0.13],[0.116,0.372]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>diet<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.value<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":4,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":1,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[1,2,3,4]},{\"name\":\"diet\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"p.value\",\"targets\":4}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[4,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n### LMM\n\n\nResearch Question 1: Did the diet change the microbiota?\n\n-   The interaction term (Treatment:Timepoint) tests whether the effect of time on Alpha diversity depends on the diet group.\n\n-   Post-hoc analysis within each diet group identifies specific changes in Alpha diversity over time.\n\nResearch Question 2: Was the microbiota equal between the diet groups before and after diet?\n\n-   The main effect of diet tests for differences in Alpha diversity between diet groups at baseline.\n\n-   Post-hoc analysis across diet groups at each timepoint identifies specific differences between diets\n\nInterpret the Results\n\n-   Main Effects:\n    -   diet: Tests for differences in microbiota between Diet A and Diet B at Baseline.\n\n    -   duration: Tests for changes in microbiota over time across both diets.\n\n    -   diet:duration: Tests whether the effect of Timepoint depends on the diet group.\n\n-   Random Effects:\n    -   (1|id): Accounts for within-subject variability.\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **FDR**\n-   Statistical test: **paired Wilcoxon**\n-   Formula used: **~ diet * timepoint + (1 | id)**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](alpha_observed_files/figure-html/table-fixed-fx-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none;\">\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-top: double; text-align:center; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; padding:0.2cm;  text-align:left; \">&nbsp;</th>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-top: double; text-align:center; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; padding:0.2cm; \">y</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  text-align:left; \">Predictors</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">Estimates</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">CI</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">p</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; \">(Intercept)</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">7.80</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">7.64&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;7.95</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertica