\">&tau;<sub>00</sub> <sub>id</sub></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.21</td>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">ICC</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.97</td>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">N <sub>id</sub></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">71</td>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; border-top:1px solid;\">Observations</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left; border-top:1px solid;\" colspan=\"3\">140</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">Marginal R<sup>2</sup> / Conditional R<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.032 / 0.970</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n`````\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n#### Post-Hoc Analysis\n\n*Within-Group Comparisons*\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|contrast          |diet |   estimate|        SE|       df|    t.ratio|   p.value|\n|:-----------------|:----|----------:|---------:|--------:|----------:|---------:|\n|Baseline - Week 6 |rice | -0.0092227| 0.0198532| 67.05762| -0.4645444| 0.6437625|\n|Baseline - Week 6 |oat  |  0.0281679| 0.0201430| 67.05926|  1.3984022| 0.1665999|\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](alpha_observed_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n*Across-Group Comparisons*\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|diet |duration |   emmean|        SE|       df| lower.CL| upper.CL|\n|:----|:--------|--------:|---------:|--------:|--------:|--------:|\n|rice |Baseline | 7.798122| 0.0784384| 71.11978| 7.641725| 7.954519|\n|oat  |Baseline | 7.646941| 0.0795510| 71.11978| 7.488325| 7.805556|\n|rice |Week 6   | 7.807345| 0.0785072| 71.36113| 7.650820| 7.963870|\n|oat  |Week 6   | 7.618773| 0.0796229| 71.36823| 7.460023| 7.777522|\n\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|contrast   |duration |  estimate|        SE|       df|  t.ratio|   p.value|\n|:----------|:--------|---------:|---------:|--------:|--------:|---------:|\n|rice - oat |Baseline | 0.1511816| 0.1117181| 71.11978| 1.353241| 0.1802643|\n|rice - oat |Week 6   | 0.1885723| 0.1118176| 71.36473| 1.686427| 0.0960809|\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](alpha_observed_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n## Data Summary\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\nclass: TreeSummarizedExperiment \ndim: 1700 140 \nmetadata(0):\nassays(1): relabundance\nrownames(1700): SGB4933 SGB4285 ... SGB15018 SGB4921\nrowData names(9): kingdom phylum ... strain clade_name\ncolnames(140): AE1332 AE2332 ... VK1336 VK2336\ncolData names(18): sample id ... group observed_log2\nreducedDimNames(0):\nmainExpName: NULL\naltExpNames(20): kingdom phylum ... KO metacyc\nrowLinks: NULL\nrowTree: NULL\ncolLinks: NULL\ncolTree: NULL\n```\n\n\n:::\n:::\n",
